<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">I want to tell you about GBST, a leading provider of securities transactions and fund administration software, who came to Tricentis looking for a solution to a problem. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">The need for a competitive edge kept GBST Shares&rsquo; software in a state of constant innovation. These required an overwhelming amount of regression testing, which, done manually, took over 535 hours of work.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Tricentis worked with GBST to leverage the Tosca Testsuite to optimize their risk coverage, manage their data, and automate their testing efforts across the company&rsquo;s highly complex system environments.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">The result?</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Accelerated end-to-end testing time by 80%.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Reduced annual testing cost by 50%.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Reduced business risk by identifying bugs early in development.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Read more about GBST&rsquo;s success with Tricentis <a href="http://www.tricentis.com/resource-assets/gbst-speeds-time-to-value/">here</a>!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">If you want to hear how Tricentis&rsquo; Tosca Testsuite can help your company succeed, I am happy to speak further with you!</span></p>
